---
title: Quick Double Prawn & Spaghetti Arrabbiata with Parmesan Cheese & Pear Salad
description: A seafood pasta is just the thing we need to make dinner time feel extra special. The spiced tomato sauce is rich and warming, with a fresh pear salad on the side. Fresh prawns are the finishing touch to this taste sensation!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/660e10fd943756c4c2243a83-d227e414.jpeg
